Margaret Cushing WHITMAN
 Corporate Executive

Daughter of Hendricks Hallett Whitman, Jr.  (1921 - 1991) and Margaret Cushing (Goodhue) Whitman  (1920-2010) was born August 04, 1956 in Cold Spring Harbor, New York   USA. She is also referred to as Meg Whitman.






