Insider Activity


Individual




Margaret C. Whitman



Ms. Margaret C. Whitman is Independent Director at Procter & Gamble Co., Chairman at HP, Inc., Chief Executive Officer at Hewlett Packard Enterprise Development LP, and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co. She is on the Board of Directors at SurveyMonkey.com LLC, Zaarly, Inc., Procter & Gamble Co., The Nature Conservancy, Inc., Teach For America, Inc., and Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co.
Ms. Whitman was previously employed as Independent Director by Zipcar, Inc., Chairman by eBay, Inc., General Manager-Preschool Division by Hasbro, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by IOS Brands Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Florists Transworld Delivery, Inc., Vice President by Bain & Co., Inc., Partner by Kleiner Perkins Caufield & Byers LLC, and Senior Vice President-Marketing by Disney Consumer Products. She also served on the board at DreamWorks Animation SKG, Inc., Gap, Inc., Procter & Gamble Co., DW II Distribution Co., LLC, and eBay Foundation.
She received her undergraduate degree from Princeton University and an MBA from Harvard University.



